Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是當時…偶然出現了那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人 怪物 怪物 怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口處傳來聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它說我是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它至少該說你是魔女嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是外星人該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞爾堤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是笑點麼？
