Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這莫不正是falling love（墜入愛河）的瞬間？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她cute（可愛）的笑容讓我跳心（心跳）加速
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}可 可是第一天就遲到…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…原來不是笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了我不知道
